These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
City: paris, boston
1. City:paris is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| City   | boston | paris |

 #################################
 
